♪Yet for you, I take it all in stride♪

97
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:55,560
♪Through wind and rain, mountains high,
and roads far♪

98
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:58,800
♪My feelings are like
a returning swallow♪

99
00:07:59,210 --> 00:08:02,320
♪Twists and turns,
a thousand lives lived♪

100
