♪Awaiting your fulfillment♪

103
00:08:13,530 --> 00:08:15,530
♪My green robes rustling♪

104
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,530
♪Your fleeting beauty,
graceful as a swan♪

105
00:08:17,530 --> 00:08:20,560
♪Parting is difficult
to see or to leave♪

106
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:22,880
♪Lingering in this mortal world♪

107
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:24,970
♪Your fleeting glance back♪

108
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:28,520
♪Sets my heart's balance askew♪

109
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:30,380
♪Endless nights, lingering♪

110
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:32,250
♪Past days, countless and vast♪

111
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:35,390
♪The red thread entwined,
fate already sealed♪

112
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:39,320
♪Each at an end,
winding past distant mountains♪

113
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:42,460
♪Meeting again, brushing
away the snow of youth's hair♪

114
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:46,120
♪Only beauty remains♪

115
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:50,460
♪As the years pass,
what can we do against heaven's will?♪

116
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:54,170
♪Even with myriad charms,
looking back with lowered gaze♪

117
